{"tid":102572,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解全球最高技術既game廠Crytek會做唔住？","createTime":"2017-01-31T17:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T15:28:58.000Z","uid":80323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1443492362efa2f6714989905f99d8830bb75d7c","tid":102572,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"自稱技術最高既遊戲公司Crytek關閉曬全部工作室，只係淨低核心團隊，落得咁既下場係咪因為擴充得太快？佢之前開到全球都有工作室。CryEngine少人用又係咪原因？<br />\n<br />\nStar Citizen又棄用CryEngine，少左個大客。Crytek係咪無能力再出game？係ps4,xbox one出番個crysis1-3合集又可唔可以賺返D錢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前Crytek CEO講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://games.renren.com/news/hot/pcgame/20121215/7605.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.renren.com%2Fnews%2Fhot%2Fpcgame%2F20121215%2F7605.shtml&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9ecc6f86\" target=\"_blank\">http://games.renren.com/news/hot/pcgame/20121215/7605.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://read01.com/Q3x2e6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FQ3x2e6.html&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=aa74cf7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/Q3x2e6.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gamersky.com/news/201101/168990.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamersky.com%2Fnews%2F201101%2F168990.shtml&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=17d8531e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gamersky.com/news/201101/168990.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/117089.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F117089.htm&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ec756dc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/117089.htm</a><br />\n英文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.videogamer.com/news/crysis-3-maxes-out-consoles-says-crytek-ceo-not-even-1-left\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih